{
  "text": "We will work, for now, in the subhalo rest frame, where \u03a6 is time-independent and thus the velocity distribution f 1 is static. In [CITATION_1] it was shown, by first going to Fourier space for the variable x, that the solution to (3) is given by",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "33087173"
